name: Gochu
description: Gochu.fun is a new token launchpad on Solana allowing users to create tokens, participate in raising funds using bonding curves and utilise anti-pvp mechanisms to ensure the success of their token in graduating to an AMM pool. Creators can earn rewards and stakers earn fees from Gochu revenue. Users are able to filter and find tokens on their desired metrics to identify promising up and coming tokens and projects. Gochu provides a fully functional platform at gochu.fun.
